      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>When turning sharp corners, keep close to the inside corner. Begin the turn when the
        inside drive wheel meets the corner. </p>
            <p>
               <p>
                  <fig id="fig_y2l_tyy_5gc">
                     <image href="media/image801.png" id="image_afl_tyy_5gc" placement="inline"/>
                  </fig>
               </p>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>In narrow aisles, keep away from the stockpile when turning
into the aisle. Allow for counterweight swing.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
